  "texts": [
    "Moreover, we leveraged state-of-the-art attribution approaches in deep learning, GNNExplainer and Integrated Gradients, to explain our developed model.",
    "The explanations were visualized as saliency maps of both molecules and genes.",
    "Remarkably, those saliency maps could be supported by the SAR studies of the drugs.",
    "Consequently, we claim that our model is able to capture the significant functional groups of drugs and their potential targeted genes, and thus reveal the comprehensive mechanism of action of drugs.",
    "In the future, we intend to extend this study to a multi-omics level."
  ],
